WordBridge - WordPress.com to Joomla Bridge
===========================================

This is WordBridge, Cognidox Ltd's WordPress.com to Joomla bridge. 
It can be used to connect a Joomla site with a wordpress.com hosted blog.

It is distributed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3:
http://www.opensource.org/licenses/agpl-v3.html

This repository holds:

    joomla_1.5/com_wordbridge - Joomla 1.5 component and plugin sources
    joomla_1.6/com_wordbridge - Joomla 1.6 component and plugin sources

Installation packages for the Joomla components are provided in the Files 
section of the Github repository.

More information about installation and usage can be found on the Cognidox
project page: 
http://www.cognidox.com/opensource/wordbridge-wordpress-to-joomla-bridge



